TRACKER
    - role: connect PEERs between themselves
    - platforms:
        - linux
        - windows
        - macos

    - features:
        - announce: to receive an announce from a PEER
        - contact: to receive feedback/request/report from a PEER
        - vote: to receive an up/down vote from PEER

PEER
    - role: listen/stream audio files
    - platforms:
        - linux
        - android
        - windows
        - ios
        - macos

    - features
        - announce: to send an announce of the LOCAL to the TRACKER
        - search: to search a song/album/artist/playlist/genre from a PROVIDER
        - stream: to stream from a PROVIDER
        - download: to download a song/album/playlist from PEER/PROVIDER
        - delete: to song/album/playlist delete from the LOCAL
        - contact: to send a feedback/request/report in the TRACKER
        - vote: to up/down vote

LOCAL
    - role: local node and its file system

PROVIDER
    - youtube - audio
    - lrclib - lyrics
    - aoty - metadata
    - discogs - metadata
    - musicbrainz - metadata
    - songstats - metadata
    - isrcfinder - metadata
    - upcfinder - metadata
    - insifinder - metadata

peer tries to get a song and when it's not available, it download it and announce it.
